  <!-- EN: A lightweight multi-barrel gatling gun originally designed for aircraft, modified for ground-based platforms. It boasts an extremely high rate of fire for rapid enemy suppression, but the lack of an effective rapid cooling system prevents it from sustaining fire for extended periods. -->
